player<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後你係點樣知佢係player?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n憑我同佢相處 可以<span style=\"color: red;\">做過男女朋友嘅嘢</span>都當冇事發生<br />\n對我又忽冷忽熱 <br />\n我見佢平時唔少嘢都會暪住人<br />\n莫講話個ig了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n扑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但攬過錫過</blockquote><br />\n絲打好慘比player...係咪同佢攬過錫過先知比人玩?<br />\n唔通真係要出動攬同錫黎試佢係咪player<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本身都抱住一絲希望嘅<br />\n但攬完錫完之後佢都可以絕口不提<br />\n關係亦冇因此而改變過<br />\n雖然當時大家都唔太清醒<br />\n見佢當冇事發生咁<br />\n我之後都唔敢提呢件事<br />\n我個心因為咁涼咗一大截<br />\n明白到佢係果啲冇手尾跟想唔洗負責果種<br />\n或者係對我先係咁掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講返正題 player冇絕對嘅signal<br />\n只不過咁啱我果個係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1429719b60bdcc387222b443f31736dd4da65198","tid":470752,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T14:37:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自己唔擺姐 人地會tag ga嘛</blockquote><br />\n合照都未必會tag人"},{"pid":"d3a4d6809509f35f762f3a551035102257c6f8bf","tid":470752,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T15:15:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好撚奇咩，你又唔知其他人會唔會介意自己比人post上其他人ig，所以咪淨係post關於自己既野囉</blockquote><br />\n但大部份人IG都會好多合照...<br />\n我唔太相信依類人整係POST自己野係為左尊重其他朋友所以先唔合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母 我就係一張自己嘅相都無<br />\n關你撚事咩 收皮啦陷家鏟<br />\n祝你全家比火燒撚死"},{"pid":"fed3d9e735c55dc321b6b3a606b1ad250b6ce1de","tid":470752,"uid":92499,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T06:47:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>大家唔好屌樓主住<br />\n我發覺好多player個fb ig都真係會扮到好健康生活好正經咁<br />\